[I] Command-line tool for everything at Exoscale

[T] exoscale is a tool to manage your Exoscale infrastructure easily from the
[T] command-line with exo.

[U] https://github.com/exoscale/cli

[A] Exoscale Authors
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/base
[F] CROSS

[L] APL
[V] 1.95.0

[D] 8c9a5e00f215661293f14e94b69ccdf94e76f02266c4ab142c5cc7d2 exoscale-1.95.0.tar.gz https://github.com/exoscale/cli/archive/refs/tags/v1.95.0/

. $base/package/*/*/go-conf.in
hook_add postmake 5 "install -v cli $root$bindir/exo"
